<mjml>
  <mj-body>
    <mj-section full-width="full-width" background-color="#f8fafc">
      <mj-column width="500px" background-color="#fff" border="1px solid #eaeaea" border-radius="10px">
        <mj-divider border-width="0px" padding="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="24px" align="center" color="#000" font-family="helvetica">
          Soap 账号注册 - 邮件验证
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="0px" padding="20px" />
        <mj-text>Hello, <mj-text font-weight="700">${username}</mj-text>:</mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="0px" padding="10px" />
        <mj-text>
          要完成注册过程，请单击下面的按钮：
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="0px" padding="10px" />
        <mj-button font-family="Helvetica" href="${host}/validatoremail?identifier=${identifier}&verificationToken=${verificationToken}&id=${id}" background-color="#05f" color="white" width="120px">
          验证
        </mj-button>
        <mj-divider border-width="0px" padding="10px" />
        <mj-divider border-color="#05f" border-style="dashed" border-width="1px"></mj-divider>
        <mj-text>
          或者将此URL复制并粘贴到您的浏览器中：
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button href="${host}/validatoremail?identifier=${identifier}&verificationToken=${verificationToken}&id=${id}" align="left" background-color="#fff" color="#05f" padding="0" text-align="left">
          ${host}/validatoremail?identifier=${identifier}&verificationToken=${verificationToken}&id=${id}
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
